    - Text: 'Finally, you make it to the docks. Instead of the normal bevy of merchant
        vessels, you can only see barges taking on people, most of them laden with
        as many of their world possessions as possible. The barges will likely take
        these peopel via the river to a proper port city. Most people with a desire
        to leave Paris, and the means to do so, are leaving France altogether.


        You wonder if they have the right idea.'
      Background: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ef95bab0adcb64b40bb571955727dbce, type: 3}
      Character1:
        AvatarID: 
        Pose: 
        Name: 
      Character2:
        AvatarID: 
        Pose: 
        Name: 
      Speaker: 0
      Rewards: []
      Music:
        Name: 
        Parameters: []
      AmbientSFX:
        Name: event:/Ambient SFX/Amb_LargeParty_outdoor
        Parameters: []
      OneShotSFX:
        Name: 
        Parameters: []
    - Text: You spot Ludovico walking down from a gangplank, and peering into the
        crowd. When he spots you, his face blossoms into an exuberant smile.
      Background: {fileID: 0}
      Character1:
        AvatarID: 
        Pose: 
        Name: 
      Character2:
        AvatarID: 
        Pose: 
        Name: 
      Speaker: 0
