    - Text: You stay on the dock for a while, and watch his boat disappear into the
        distance. Part of you wants to watch him for as long as you can, and another
        part of you simply isn't ready for the trials of getting home through all
        of this chaos.
      Background: {fileID: 0}
      Character1:
        AvatarID: 
        Pose: 
        Name: 
      Character2:
        AvatarID: 
        Pose: 
        Name: 
      Speaker: 0
      Rewards: []
      Music:
