        Parameters: []
    - Text: As the boat starts to leave, you're about to turn and head home, until
        you see Ludovico run to the back of the boat. He starts shouting, loud enough
        for everyone to hear.
      Background: {fileID: 0}
      Character1:
        AvatarID: 
        Pose: 
        Name: 
      Character2:
        AvatarID: 
        Pose: 
        Name: 
      Speaker: 0
      Rewards: []
      Music:
        Name: 
        Parameters: []
      AmbientSFX:
        Name: 
        Parameters: []
      OneShotSFX:
        Name: 
        Parameters: []
    - Text: '"Yvette! Please stay safe! You''re the best woman I''ve ever met!"'
      Background: {fileID: 0}
      Character1:
        AvatarID: 
        Pose: 
        Name: Ludovico
      Character2:
        AvatarID: 
        Pose: 
        Name: 
      Speaker: 2
      Rewards: []
      Music:
        Name: 
        Parameters: []
      AmbientSFX:
        Name: 
        Parameters: []
      OneShotSFX:
        Name: 
        Parameters: []
    - Text: '"You''re the greatest blessing I''ve ever had!"'
      Background: {fileID: 0}
      Character1:
        AvatarID: 
        Pose: 
        Name: Ludovico
      Character2:
        AvatarID: 
        Pose: 
        Name: 
      Speaker: 2
      Rewards: []
      Music:
        Name: 
        Parameters: []
      AmbientSFX:
        Name: 
        Parameters: []
      OneShotSFX:
        Name: 
        Parameters: []
    - Text: There's a hesitation in his voice, as he realizes that the entire dock
        is watching you both. He chooses his next words carefully.
      Background: {fileID: 0}
      Character1:
        AvatarID: 
        Pose: 
        Name: 
      Character2:
        AvatarID: 
        Pose: 
        Name: 
      Speaker: 0
      Rewards: []
      Music:
        Name: 
        Parameters: []
      AmbientSFX:
